lead_paragraph: Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton says he has no concerns about Mercedes team mate Nico Rosberg's five-race winning streak or his own poor starts this season.

headline.print_headline: Remember the 'Rope a Dope', Hamilton Reminds Rosberg
